; A file that ends mid-declaration: name parsed, no parameter list, no
; period. Expected: a rendered "Incomplete message declaration" diagnostic,
; exit 1, in all 4 modes. Before the F21 fix the incomplete-declaration
; error paths dereferenced the never-created declaration object (SIGSEGV,
; exit 139) — reachable from any truncated file, and from any non-ASCII
; byte cutting the token stream short mid-declaration (#local and #functor
; had the same defect; #query already degraded cleanly).
#message m
